description:
OUR QUEENS ARE BACK IN ACTION! Danny recaps the season 11 premiere of The Real Housewives of New York!!! The episode starts with a look back on the most iconic moments from the first 10 seasons before diving into the new episode which featured the introduction of DIY/tool superstar Barbara K & so much more!
